Q4. Running Total as % of Grand Total
Compute the cumulative (running) sum of transactions ordered by date, and show it as a percentage of the overall total. Round to 2 decimal places.
SELECT
  txn_date,
  amount,
  SUM(amount) OVER (ORDER BY txn_date ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW) AS running_total,
  ROUND(
    SUM(amount) OVER (ORDER BY txn_date ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW)
    * 100.0 / SUM(amount) OVER (),
  2) AS running_pct
FROM transactions
ORDER BY txn_date;
