Q6. % of Category Leader
For each product, show its revenue and what percentage of the top-ranked product's revenue (within its category) it represents. Round to 2 decimal places.

SELECT
  category,
  product_name,
  revenue,
  FIRST_VALUE(revenue) OVER (PARTITION BY category ORDER BY revenue DESC) AS category_leader_revenue,
  ROUND(
    revenue * 100.0 / FIRST_VALUE(revenue) OVER (PARTITION BY category ORDER BY revenue DESC),
  2) AS pct_of_leader
FROM products
ORDER BY category, revenue DESC;

