Q7. Dept Headcount as % of Company
At the individual employee row level, show each employee's name, their department, and their department's headcount as a percentage of the total company headcount. Round to 2 decimal places.

SELECT
  name,
  dept,
  COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY dept) AS dept_headcount,
  COUNT(*) OVER () AS total_headcount,
  ROUND(
    COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY dept) * 100.0 / COUNT(*) OVER (),
  2) AS dept_pct_of_company
FROM employees
ORDER BY dept, name;
